<section class="px-5 md:px-0 flex justify-center items-start py-5 mt-24  mb-10  min-h-[682px]  shadow-[0px_4px_4px_rgba(0,0,0,0.25)] ">
  <div class="w-full max-w-[1080px] flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-20">
    <div class="flex flex-col-reverse md:flex-col  gap-5 w-full md:w-1/2 px-5">
      <section class="w-full text-xl font-bold text-white min-w-60 ">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold font-titulos">Comunicate con Nosotros</h2>
        <p class="mt-5 text-base font-parrafos font-thin text-justify">
          Recupera tu tiempo libre y disfruta de un espacio impecable. En Soma,
          nos encargamos de dejar tu hogar o negocio reluciente para que t√∫ te
          enfoques en lo que realmente importa.
        </p>
        <address class="mt-5 leading-7 not-italic font-parrafos text-base font-bold">
          Telefono: 099878767<br />
          Instagram: @Somaec<br />
          Alborada Decima Etapainfosoma@soma.com
        </address>
      </section>
      <div class="max-w-[500px] mb-12 md:mb-0">
          <img
              src="/img/chofer.png"
              alt="Contact illustration"
              class="rounded-3xl"
            />
        </div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="flex flex-col justify-start items-center w-full md:w-1/2">
        <div class="max-w-full text-white w-[413px]">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-titulos">Separa hoy tu cita</h2>
          <p class="mt-3 text-base">Deja eso que te quita tu tiempo</p>
        </div>

        <form class="flex flex-col mt-4 w-full text-base whitespace-nowrap max-w-[413px] text-zinc-500 max-md:mt-10">
          <div class="flex gap-3.5 w-full">
            <input
              type="text"
              placeholder="Nombre"
              class="basis-1/2 gap-2 pl-4 py-4 bg-white rounded-3xl min-h-[52px]"
              required
            />
            <input
              type="tel"
              placeholder="Numero"
              class="basis-1/2 gap-2 pl-4 py-4 bg-white rounded-3xl min-h-[52px]"
              required
            />
          </div>

          <input
            type="email"
            placeholder="Correo"
            class="gap-2.5 self-stretch px-5 py-4 mt-4 bg-white rounded-3xl min-h-[52px] w-full"
            required
          />

          <textarea
            placeholder="Mensaje"
            class="gap-2.5 px-5 pt-2.5 pb-24 mt-4 bg-white rounded-3xl min-h-[127px] w-full"
            required
          ></textarea>

          <button
            type="submit"
            class="gap-2.5 self-stretch px-2.5 py-4 mt-4 text-white bg-sky-900 rounded-3xl min-h-[52px] w-full hover:bg-sky-800 transition-colors"
          >
            Enviar
          </button>
        </form>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
